      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yeah, it shouldn\u0027t mutate the input param, but go/goprotoapi-findings#message-shallowcopy.\nI can use proto.Clone(), but I don\u0027t think it\u0027s a good idea, either.\n\nAnother solution is to exclude those fields in the ProprtyLoadSaver interface. \n: https://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/master:go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/buildbucket/appengine/model/build.go;l\u003d122\n\nWDYT? smut@ nodir@?",
