      "message": "input is not a valid mask for UpdateMask.\nhttps://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/master:go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/buildbucket/proto/builds_service.proto;l\u003d193-200\n\nIf input is not in the mask, mask.Merge() won\u0027t merge it, whether the request.Input actually has value or not.",
